{
  "arquivo": "op_02_03",
  "total": 59,
  "dialogos": [
    {
      "id": 0,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Hey, sorry to have kept you waiting.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "...No way.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Yes, way.\\nI've come to see you, Miku.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Woah!\\nHey, Miku?! Are you alright?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "*sniff* Oo-ooohh...\\nI-I'm okay...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "How are you okay?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "O-ooooohh, uh...\\nS-sorr—I...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "It's okay, don't say anything right now.\\nI'll stay by your side until you calm down.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Futaro...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "*sniff*...oooohh...!\\nOoooooohh!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Hey... Why are you crying even more...?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "It's just, it's just...you, Futaro...!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Huh me?\\nUm, so what should I do then?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "...Hold my hand.\\nAnd just stay by my side... That's all I need...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Sure.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Have you calmed down?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Uh...\\nI'm alright now.\\nSorry for bothering you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Just so you know, you haven't bothered me or anything.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "It's always been that way.\\nI've never been troubled by you, Miku.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Really?\\nI feel like I've troubled you quite a bit.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "That's not true.\\nAfter all, you've always faced things head-on\\nand never ran away, Miku.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Yeah?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "That's right, I think you've often felt more anxious\\ncompared to your other sisters.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "But,\\neven when you were suffering from anxiety,\\nyou never tried to run away from your problems.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "You tried to find your own way of fighting\\nand made relentless effort to move forward.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Futaro...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "So, about me, yeah?\\nI think I'm attracted to your willpower,\\nor rather, your earnestness... Yes, that's the word.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I'd like to challenge the unknown with you and continuously grow together. ",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "For me, you, Miku, are a special person.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I'm sorry for my...delayed answer.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Maybe it's rather quick for you, Futaro?\\nTo be honest, I thought you'd keep me waiting\\nuntil graduation or something.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Don't give me that.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "You guys showed your determination in this way.\\nI couldn't leave the answer hanging, right?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Yeah.\\nI'm glad you answered properly.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Hey... Futaro...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "What is it?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I love you, Futaro.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "You're blushing.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "...Me too.\\nI love you too, Miku.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "~~~~~.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 43,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "You blushed too, didn't you?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 44,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I-I love you more.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 45,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "What are you talking about?\\nI-I'm the one who l-loves you more, you know?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 46,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "No, it's me.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 47,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Me!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 48,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 49,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 50,
      "personagem": "Both",
      "texto_en": "Pft!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 51,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Teehee!\\nWhat are we doing?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 52,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "You've got that right.\\nJust what are we doing?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 53,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "But...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 54,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I think this is definitely\\nwhat they call happiness.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 55,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "That's probably true.\\nHonestly, I don't feel it yet.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 56,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "But with you here, Miku,\\nI feel like I can do anything.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 57,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Me too.\\nIf you're with me, Futaro,\\nI feel like I can go anywhere.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 58,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Hand in hand, we can go anywhere,\\nas far as we can go.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    }
  ]
}